<l>camaṉceytu cīrtūkkuṅ kōlpō lamaintorupāṟ</l>
<l>kōṭāmai cāṉṟōrk kaṇi</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Like the even-weighing balance pole, to calmly weigh each side</l>
<l>unbending is the ornament of the wise.</l>
